---
import Hero2 from '~/components/widgets/Hero2.astro';
import Content from '~/components/widgets/Content.astro';
import Testimonials from '~/components/widgets/Testimonials.astro';
import Contact from '~/components/sections/Contact.astro'
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';

const metadata = {
  title: 'Expert tree health & insect control treatments in Roseburg, OR and near you',
	description: 'Expert tree health & insect control treatments in Roseburg, OR. We are a local tree service company that offers tree removal, tree trimming, stump grinding, and more. Call us today for a free estimate.',
};
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <!-- Hero2 Widget ******************* -->

  <Hero2
    tagline="Healthy & Safe Trees"
    title="Roseburg, OR Tree Health & Insect Control Treatments Experts"
    subtitle="For the control of insects and diseases. Serving Roseburg, OR and surrounding areas. Call us today for a free estimate."
    actions={[
      { variant: 'primary', text: 'Get a FREE Estimate', href: 'get-a-free-estimate', icon: 'tabler:square-rounded-arrow-right' },
    ]}
    image={{
      src: '~/assets/images/services/tree-injections.jpg',
      alt: 'Tree Health & Insect Control Treatments Image',
    }}
  />

  <!-- Content Widget **************** -->

  <Content
    isReversed
    image={{
      src: '~/assets/images/hero.jpg',
      alt: 'Professional tree removal services in Roseburg, OR',
    }}
    callToAction={{
      target: '_self',
      text: 'Get a FREE Estimate',
      href: 'get-a-free-estimate',
      icon: 'tabler:square-rounded-arrow-right',
    }}
  >
    <Fragment slot="content">
      <!-- <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight dark:text-white sm:text-3xl mb-2">What we offer as professional arborists</h3> -->
      <p class="text-xl text-muted mb-6 dark:text-slate-300">Heat stresses evergreen trees because the dry soil conditions make it more difficult for them to absorb water to make sap which is one of their natural defenses. When trees become stressed from abiotic factors, they become more susceptible to biotic attacks. One of the signs of stress in an evergreen tree is needles changing color. A long slow soak with a garden hose can help trees suffering from heat stress to survive. The good news is that most bark beetles do not attack healthy trees. </p>
      <p class="text-xl text-muted mb-6 dark:text-slate-300">If your trees are being attacked by disease or insects we have treatments that can help. But it is important to act quickly to diagnose the issues before it is too late. ğŸ¤’ğŸ¤•ğŸ˜µ With bark beetles, chemical treatments are only affective if they are applied before bark beetles are present or during the early stages of an infestation cycle. The first sign of a bark beetle infestation is saw dust around the trunk of the tree. It is especially important now to be on the lookout for a new Invader to Oregon; Emerald Ash Borer(EAB). Injections can be administered any time of year. Trees benefit the most if they are administered in the early spring.</p>
    </Fragment>
  </Content>

